13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 8-101.2, as
14 amended by Section 1, Chapter 193, O.S.L. 2022 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15 Section 8-101.2), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 8-101.2. A. Except as provided in subsection B of this
17 section, on and after January 1, 2022, the transfer of a student
18 from the district in which the student resides to another school
19 district furnishing instruction in the grade the student is entitled
20 to pursue shall be granted at any time in the year unless the number
21 of transfers exceeds the capacity of a grade level for each school
22 site within a school district. If the capacity of a grade level for
23 each school site within a school district is insufficient to enroll
24 all eligible students, the school district shall select transfer
